name: Klaus Zorn (cyclops)
description:
The same creep showed up before WWI, was suppressed by Galaxi Jade, but rose up again before WWII. Klaus Zorn is bonded to the Germanic patch of earth, and whenever he awakens, blood and despair abound. 

There are whispers of his return, and let us hope he is not the shadow at the foot of Merkel's bed!
